Criteria for grading: 

Your Codemates team used Issues to clearly delineate work (30%)
Was there stated acceptance criteria?
Is there a clear discussion happening amongst the group?
Have all the issues been closed when resolved?
Your Codemates team used Pull Requests to supply multiple solutions (40%)
Did every team member commit to the Pull Requests?
Did the team use the reviews feature of GitHub to get explicit approval? 
Did at least TWO people approve each Pull Request? 
Work collaboratively on changes until objective is completed (30%)
Are there (3) fully completed recipes on the main/master branch?
Was there healthy disagreement? Discussion of style in the Pull Requests? 
